        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Commons Preservation Society, | 1, Great College Street, Westminster, S.W.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>30<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. May <hi rend="italic">18</hi>78</date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir,</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
                    <p>Knockholt &amp; Chevening Footpath Fund.<ref target="#foot.f1"/></p>
<p>As Treasurer of the above Fund I have been requested to make a call of one-third of the amount guaranteed towards defraying the expenses incurred in resisting the closing of this footpath. This sum will be sufficient to meet the liabilities incurred.</p>
<p>As you kindly guaranteed £<hi rend="underline">7.0.0.</hi>* I shall be glad if you will favour me with one-third of that sum. When the accounts have been closed a Balance Sheet will be sent to each subscriber.</p>
<p>I am, | Yours truly, | Edward W. Fithian</p> 
